{"tid":518414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【政府斥資4億7千萬元建飛行服務隊分部】","createTime":"2018-01-03T09:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T13:50:04.000Z","uid":28366,"like":36,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b0eee840f2f66597ed66f5393dc6e8a4873deeca","tid":518414,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"政府建議在啟德興建飛行服務隊分部，造價超過四億元。<br />\n<br />\n項目建議在前啟德跑道末端，佔地約7400平方米，包括直升機坪、直升機庫、辦公大樓、航空策劃中心及其他輔助設施，整體工程造價為4億6900萬元，稍後向立法會財委會申請撥款，期望今年第四季動工，到2021年底完成。<br />\n<br />\n政府指，現時位於赤鱲角的飛行服務隊總部航道受到附近建築物影響，難以在不利天氣下支援緊急服務，所以有必要另設分部。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5a4c8a83e603832213bad415/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5a4c8a83e603832213bad415%2F&d=ryJDW5LW9OMZ1e8iLawrI%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=de982a99\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5a4c8a83e603832213bad415/</a>"},{"pid":"430d6dadb6996d41aa7f1e5e16bc5e9c5f69eaf6","tid":518414,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694328aba66887abc23c8f4158d96c8f23757222","tid":518414,"uid":6352,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"實政"},{"pid":"04dbd4252465646f2c5275b7d18c3c2d752657e0","tid":518414,"uid":28366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f2c66cbf9e0ad9fba4d7bdc5078ddcdd672a33","tid":518414,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"24b6e8a4716da1210661d0532dc23fbe3752d303","tid":518414,"uid":82587,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T00:22:06.000Z","msg":"地王位置,正"},{"pid":"3358da302b968c806758a653114d0340a95cadfb","tid":518414,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":